ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details for an organization or a particular human that is responsible for the device.

ivardefs.name: definition
ivardefs.desc: The reference to the definition for the device.

ivardefs.name: deviceName_
ivardefs.desc: This represents the manufacturer's name of the device as provided by the device, from a UDI label, or by a person describing the Device.  This typically would be used when a person provides the name(s) or when the device represents one of the names availa

ivardefs.name: distinctIdentifier
ivardefs.desc: The distinct identification string as required by regulation for a human cell, tissue, or cellular and tissue-based product.

ivardefs.name: expirationDate
ivardefs.desc: The date and time beyond which this device is no longer valid or should not be used (if applicable).

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Unique instance identifiers assigned to a device by manufacturers other organizations or owners.

ivardefs.name: location
ivardefs.desc: The place where the device can be found.

ivardefs.name: lotNumber
ivardefs.desc: Lot number assigned by the manufacturer.

ivardefs.name: manufactureDate
ivardefs.desc: The date and time when the device was manufactured.

ivardefs.name: manufacturer
ivardefs.desc: A name of the manufacturer.

ivardefs.name: modelNumber
ivardefs.desc: The model number for the device.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Descriptive information, usage information or implantation information that is not captured in an existing element.

ivardefs.name: owner
ivardefs.desc: An organization that is responsible for the provision and ongoing maintenance of the device.

ivardefs.name: parent
ivardefs.desc: The parent device.

ivardefs.name: partNumber
ivardefs.desc: The part number of the device.

ivardefs.name: patient
ivardefs.desc: Patient information, If the device is affixed to a person.

ivardefs.name: property_
ivardefs.desc: The actual configuration settings of a device as it actually operates, e.g., regulation status, time properties.

ivardefs.name: safety_
ivardefs.desc: Provides additional safety characteristics about a medical device.  For example devices containing latex.

ivardefs.name: serialNumber
ivardefs.desc: The serial number assigned by the organization when the device was manufactured.

ivardefs.name: specialization_
ivardefs.desc: The capabilities supported on a  device, the standards to which the device conforms for a particular purpose, and used for the communication.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: Status of the Device availability.

ivardefs.name: statusReason_
ivardefs.desc: Reason for the dtatus of the Device availability.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The kind or type of device.

ivardefs.name: udiCarrier_
ivardefs.desc: Unique device identifier (UDI) assigned to device label or package.  Note that the Device may include multiple udiCarriers as it either may include just the udiCarrier for the jurisdiction it is sold, or for multiple jurisdictions it could have been sold.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: A network address on which the device may be contacted directly.

ivardefs.name: version_
ivardefs.desc: The actual design of the device or software version running on the device.

properties.desc: A type of a manufactured item that is used in the provision of healthcare without being substantially changed through that activity. The device may be a medical or non-medical device.
